  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK216">
<l>payaṉmara muḷḷūrp paḻuttaṟṟāṟ celva</l>
<l>nayaṉuṭai yāṉkaṭ paṭiṉ</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The wealth of a man (possessed of the virtue) of benevolence is like the ripening of a fruitful tree in the midst of a town.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
